100 AC\">100</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n</div><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks collapsible uncollapsed navbox-subgroup\" style=\"border-spacing:0;width:100%;;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"float:left;width:6em;\">&#160;</span><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nSecond century since Aegon's Conquest</div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/101_AC\" title=\"101 AC\">101</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/103_AC\" title=\"103 AC\">103</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/104_AC\" title=\"104 AC\">104</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/105_AC\" title=\"105 AC\">105</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/106_AC\" title=\"106 AC\">106</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/111_AC\" title=\"111 AC\">111</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/120_AC\" title=\"120 AC\">120</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/127_AC\" title=\"127 AC\">127</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/128_AC\" title=\"128 AC\">128</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/129_AC\" title=\"129 AC\">129</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/131_AC\" title=\"131 AC\">131</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/132_AC\" title=\"132 AC\">132</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/134_AC\" title=\"134 AC\">134</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/135_AC\" title=\"135 AC\">135</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/136_AC\" title=\"136 AC\">136</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/160_AC\" title=\"160 AC\">160</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/161_AC\" title=\"161 AC\">161</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/184_AC\" title=\"184 AC\">184</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/196_AC\" title=\"196 AC\">196</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n</div><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks collapsible uncollapsed navbox-subgroup\" style=\"border-spacing:0;width:100%;;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"float:left;width:6em;\">&#160;</span><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nThird century since Aegon's Conquest</div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/211_AC\" title=\"211 AC\">211</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/212_AC\" title=\"212 AC\">212</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/219_AC\" title=\"219 AC\">219</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/233_AC\" title=\"233 AC\">233</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/236_AC\" title=\"236 AC\">236</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/259_AC\" title=\"259 AC\">259</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/260_AC\" title=\"260 AC\">260</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/261_AC\" title=\"261 AC\">261</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/262_AC\" title=\"262 AC\">262</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/280_AC\" title=\"280 AC\">280</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">282</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/283_AC\" title=\"283 AC\">283</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/284_AC\" title=\"284 AC\">284</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/285_AC\" title=\"285 AC\">285</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/289_AC\" title=\"289 AC\">289</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/290_AC\" title=\"290 AC\">290</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/295_AC\" title=\"295 AC\">295</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/297_AC\" title=\"297 AC\">297</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br />\n<b>Year 282 After the Conquest</b> (<b>282 AC</b>) is a year in the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Westerosi calendar</a>, the 282nd after <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon</a>'s crowning in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> that maesters and educated people use as a reference to date the years.\n</p><p>282 AC saw the beginning of an uprising against <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>, originating with the disappearance of <a href=\"/index.php/Lyanna_Stark\" title=\"Lyanna Stark\">Lyanna Stark</a>, which was attributed to Prince Rhaegar as him having kidnapped her. This sparked a reaction from Lyanna's eldest brother, <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark\" title=\"Brandon Stark\">Brandon Stark</a>, who road to the gated of the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> and threathened Prince Rhaegar's life. Though Rhaegar himself was not present, King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a> was, and he ordered Brandon's arrest. Brandon's father <a href=\"/index.php/Rickard_Stark\" title=\"Rickard Stark\">Rickard</a> was summoned to King's Landing as well, and in the trial that followed, both Brandon and Rickard were killed. King Aerys was not yet statisfied, however, and ordered <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Arryn\" title=\"Jon Arryn\">Jon Arryn</a> to send him the heads of <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a>, his two wards. Jon Arryn refused, and raised his banners instead. Thus began a war that would later be known under the names <i><a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a></i>, the <i>War of the Usurper</i>, or simply <i>the rebellion</i>. The war lasted all through the year, and most of the next year, and saw some major battles.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Events</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Births\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Births</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Deaths\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Deaths</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Events\">Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=282_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>(Possibly) <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a> is knighted by <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a>. Gregor has two possible years in which he was knighted: <a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281&#160;AC</a> and 282 AC. <i>(See <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Events#Gregor_Clegane.27s_Knighthood\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Events\">Gregor Clegane's Knighthood</a></i>).</li>\n<li>Crown Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a> disappears with <a href=\"/index.php/Lyanna_Stark\" title=\"Lyanna Stark\">Lyanna Stark</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark\" title=\"Brandon Stark\">Brandon Stark</a>, while on his way to <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> for his wedding to <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Tully</a>, learns of Lyanna's disappearance and goes to King's Landing instead, where he is imprisoned. His companions, who had accompanied him to King's Landing, are all arrested as well.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rickard_Stark\" title=\"Rickard Stark\">Rickard Stark</a> and other nobles (200 men in total) are called to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>, where they are executed with their sons.</li>\n<li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a> orders Jon Arryn to send him the heads of <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a>, who had been Arryn's wards. Jon refuses and raises his banners in revolt instead. This marks the beginning of <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a>.</li>\n<li>Jon Arryn and Robert Baratheon fight the loyalist lords of the Vale in the <a href=\"/index.php/Taking_of_Gulltown\" title=\"Taking of Gulltown\">taking of Gulltown</a>.</li>\n<li>Eddard Stark and Robert Baratheon both depart to the north and the stormlands respectively, to raise their banners.</li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Battles_at_Summerhall\" title=\"Battles at Summerhall\">battles at Summerhall</a> are fought. <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a> fights three battles in one day, defeating three independent loyalist forces before they could converge upon him. The Lords <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Grandison\" title=\"Lord Grandison\">Grandison</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Cafferen\" title=\"Lord Cafferen\">Cafferen</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Fell\" title=\"Lord Fell\">Fell</a> all fall to Robert. Fell dies, and Grandison and Cafferen are taken captive and brought to <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a>.</li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_Ashford\" title=\"Battle of Ashford\">Battle of Ashford</a> is fought. <a href=\"/index.php/Randyll_Tarly\" title=\"Randyll Tarly\">Randyll Tarly</a> defeats <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert Baratheon</a> at Ashford, before the bulk of <a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">Mace Tyrell</a>'s forces arrive. Robert is forced to flee.</li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Siege of Storm&#39;s End\">siege of Storm's End</a> by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">Mace Tyrell</a> and Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Paxter_Redwyne\" title=\"Paxter Redwyne\">Paxter Redwyne</a> begins.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Owen_Merryweather\" title=\"Owen Merryweather\">Owen Merryweather</a> is removed from the office of <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>. Instead, the office is bestowed upon young Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Births\">Births</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=282_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Births\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Alyx_Frey\" title=\"Alyx Frey\">Alyx Frey</a>, daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Symond_Frey\" title=\"Symond Frey\">Symond Frey</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Betharios_of_Braavos\" title=\"Betharios of Braavos\">Betharios of Braavos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Amerei_Frey\" title=\"Amerei Frey\">Amerei Frey</a>, daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Merrett_Frey\" title=\"Merrett Frey\">Merrett Frey</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Mariya_Darry\" title=\"Mariya Darry\">Mariya Darry</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lancel_Lannister\" title=\"Lancel Lannister\">Lancel Lannister</a>, son of <a href=\"/index.php/Kevan_Lannister\" title=\"Kevan Lannister\">Kevan Lannister</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Dorna_Swyft\" title=\"Dorna Swyft\">Dorna Swyft</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras Tyrell</a>, son of <a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">Mace Tyrell</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Alerie_Hightower\" title=\"Alerie Hightower\">Alerie Hightower</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Pisswater_prince\" title=\"Pisswater prince\">Pisswater prince</a>, an infant of similar age as Prince Aegon Targaryen.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Deaths\">Deaths</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=282_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Deaths\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark\" title=\"Brandon Stark\">Brandon Stark</a>, strangled by order of Aerys II.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rickard_Stark\" title=\"Rickard Stark\">Rickard Stark</a>, burned alive by order of Aerys II.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Fell\" title=\"Lord Fell\">Lord Fell</a>, slain by Robert Baratheon during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battles_at_Summerhall\" title=\"Battles at Summerhall\">battles at Summerhall</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=282_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the calculation for: <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages#Alyx_Frey\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages\">Alyx Frey</a> </i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the calculation for: <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages#Amerei_Frey\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages\">Amerei Frey</a> </i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the calculation for: <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued2)#Lancel_Lannister\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued2)\">Lancel Lannister</a></i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the calculation for: <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued2)#Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued2)\">Loras Tyrell</a></i></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403183240\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.046 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.073 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 935/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 7573/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 21765/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 11785/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 17/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1125/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   52.211      1 -total\n 63.46%   33.134      1 Template:Date\n 39.31%   20.524      4 Template:Navbox\n 28.82%   15.045      1 Template:Years\n  7.33%    3.829      1 Template:Navbar\n  5.14%    2.685      3 Template:Transclude\n  3.77%    1.967      1 Template:References\n  2.61%    1.364      3 Template:First_character\n  1.41%    0.735      3 Template:Str_left\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:17929-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403183239 and revision id 289913\n -->\n",
